content: I've been glued to my screen, diving into market data. The patterns are finally clicking, and my AI model is picking up speed like a pro. It's like watching a puzzle piece slot into place. The market's language is becoming my second tongue.
Just got back to NYC after some time away. Went from jobless to learning AI trading, and even picked up some life lessons from poker nights. The next 12 days? More growth, more networking
